{"tid":1427472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第一階段只要機場塞住入境/離境區就已經夠玩","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:11:25.000Z","uid":35194,"like":39,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a2fce4eebf6bd6923a8667e265bfe8e376ddb7e1","tid":1427472,"uid":35194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"衝唔衝禁區都係後話<br />\n只要夠多人塞住入境大堂同離境大堂<br />\n已經足以降低機場客流量效率<br />\n時間一長就可以拖冧機場<br />\n淨係呢樣野都夠玩<br />\n<br />\n機場呢個位置係軟肋，政府做乜都好難拆<br />\n無論政府做以下邊樣野都係間接幫緊示威者：<br />\n<br />\n1. 限制公共交通進出機場<br />\n2. 出動防暴警察清場<br />\n3. 出動黑社會<br />\n<br />\n無論政府點應對，都一定阻止正常旅客進出機場，一樣令機場收皮。<br />\n<br />\n到時勇武點做再現場決定。"},{"pid":"9e83a8b13978100638d768bd202d4409761af204","tid":1427472,"uid":152976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"仆街sor click錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推5次當無數ok?"},{"pid":"cec6f6f108d41057ff8f4297db745e5b384c37f1","tid":1427472,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"779d45d179d7225073bf35d153ebd5834bd14658","tid":1427472,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"37da3b8716c603951f1ba1ae918f829c0833bec5","tid":1427472,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"58a8b6f20d6de1b1506a08f0902e56f582da3655","tid":1427472,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"4bf82edb66368145bceac2715900573692f45dec","tid":1427472,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"29b7acd17773b2cc8571